Package com.sirqul.sdk.api.common Description

Contains API classes that fall under the Common category. Includes AccountApi, AchievementApi, AlbumApi, AlbumContestApi, AssetApi, AssetCollectionApi, AudienceApi, BaseApi, CategoryApi, ConnectionApi, EmployeeApi, FacebookApi, FavoriteApi, FilterApi, FlagApi, InviteApi, LikeApi, NoteApi, NotificationApi, RatingApi, and UserPermissionsApi.
